These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, disco, soul, electronic
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, tea, juice, mirinda
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, marigold, azalea, zinnia
1. the person who growslily is the fan of electronic##1
2. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
3. the fan of electronic is in an odd position##4
4. the person who growsmarigold is on the left or right of the person who growszinnia##3
5. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
6. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the fan of soul##1
7. the person who growsmarigold is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who growszinnia is between the person drinking mirinda and the fan of classical##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Music-Genre         | electronic      | classical | disco | soul |
| Beverage   | juice | fanta  | tea   | mirinda    |
| Flower     | lily     | azalea    | zinnia    | marigold      |

