.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, alhambra, swisher, dunhill
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, animation, mystery, comedy
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, writer, designer, pilot
1. the writer is on the left or right of the swisher-smoker##3
2. the dunhill-smoker is the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the swisher-smoker is in an even position##4
4. the teacher is on the far right##1
5. the pilot is on the far left##1
6. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
7. the person watching sports movies is between the dunhill-smoker and the alhambra-smoker##2
8. the person watching comedy movies is between the person watching animation movies and the swisher-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Cigar         | dunhill | swisher   | alhambra | blend  |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery     | sports | comedy  | animation |
| Job     | pilot        | designer  | writer    | teacher |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
House: cape-cod, palace, victorian, art-deco
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, security-guard, architect, lawyer
4 different games are played: domino, snooker, chess, canasta
1. the lawyer is between the cape-cod house and the art-deco house##2
2. the security-guard is the person playing canasta##1
3. the person playing domino is the victorian house##1
4. the person playing domino is on the right of the art-deco house##1
5. the art-deco house is in an odd position##4
6. the architect is between the palace house and the entrepreneur##2
7. the lawyer is on the left of the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| House          | cape-cod | palace   | art-deco     | victorian     |
| Job   | security-guard  | lawyer | architect   | entrepreneur  |
| Game     | canasta      | snooker | chess | domino |

