.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, van, tram, subway
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, video-games, filmmaking, magic-tricks
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, bolivar, bongani, prince
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the van is the bolivar-smoker##1
3. the prince-smoker is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the davidoff-smoker##1
6. the person driving the tram is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Transport   | taxi  | subway   | tram     | van |
| Hobby   | filmmaking  | magic-tricks      | card-games        | video-games     |
| Cigar         | bongani | davidoff | prince | bolivar   |

