.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, chess, hiking, fishing
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, montecristo, old-henry, fonseca
There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, turquise, purple, brown
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is the fonseca-smoker##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an odd position##4
3. the person who likes yellow is the fonseca-smoker##1
4. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
5. the person who likes yellow is in an even position##4
6. the montecristo-smoker is on the far left##1
7. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far right##1
8. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the person who likes purple##3
9. the alhambra-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Hobby   | sudoku   | fishing   | hiking | chess |
| Cigar         | montecristo      | fonseca | alhambra      | old-henry |
| Color     | turquise | yellow        | brown       | purple  |

