.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
House: craftsman, ranch-style, victorian, futuristic
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, indian, colombian, japanese
City: san-francisco, rome, boston, liverpool
1. the ranch-style house is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the colombian##1
3. the person traveling to san-francisco is the ranch-style house##1
4. the victorian house is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
5. the indian is on the far right##1
6. the futuristic house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
7. the futuristic house is in an even position##4
8. the japanese is on the right of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| House    | victorian   | futuristic      | ranch-style       | craftsman |
| Nationality   | brazilian | japanese | colombian     | indian |
| City     | liverpool     | rome  | san-francisco | boston |

