.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
4 different games are played: snooker, backgammon, bridge, canasta
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, trike, helicopter, bus
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, oliveros, swisher, fonseca
1. the swisher-smoker is the person driving the bike##1
2. the oliveros-smoker is between the person driving the bus and the ritmeester-smoker##2
3. the person driving the bus is the person playing backgammon##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
5. the person playing snooker is in an even position##4
6. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
7. the person driving the bike is the person playing snooker##1
8. the swisher-smoker is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Game      | bridge   | canasta          | backgammon | snooker        |
| Transport   | helicopter     | trike | bus   | bike     |
| Cigar           | ritmeester | oliveros         | fonseca         | swisher |

