.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, helicopter, van, trike
4 different games are played: poker, mah-jongg, scrabble, backgammon
4 different pets are kept: rat, goldfish, ferret, cat
1. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
2. the person playing scrabble is the person driving the roller##1
3. the person playing backgammon is the person driving the van##1
4. the person driving the van is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is between the person playing poker and the person driving the roller##2
6. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
7. the person driving the roller is in an even position##4
8. the person driving the roller is between the person driving the helicopter and the person driving the van##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Transport         | helicopter | roller      | van       | trike    |
| Game           | mah-jongg  | scrabble  | backgammon | poker |
| Pet   | cat      | ferret | goldfish         | rat    |

