.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, amber, coral, green
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, photography, magic-tricks, board-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, romance, superhero, crime
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes black is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
3. the person who likes green is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
4. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person who likes black##1
5. the person who likes amber is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3
6. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who likes black##1
8. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
9. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Color   | amber         | black  | coral     | green         |
| Hobby        | board-games | photography | rock-climbing | magic-tricks         |
| Movie-Genre      | romance         | superhero  | epic   | crime |

