.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, chef, designer, scientist
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, ritmeester, dannemann, cain
4 different games are played: bridge, snooker, domino, mah-jongg
 1. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the designer##3
 2. the aristoff-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person playing snooker is on the right of the chef##1
 4. the dannemann-smoker is between the chef and the mechanic##2
 5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the chef##3
 6. the person playing mah-jongg is the designer##1
 7. the cain-smoker is on the far right##1
 8. the mechanic is in an odd position##4
 9. the ritmeester-smoker is between the scientist and the designer##2
10. the person playing domino is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Job   | mechanic  | designer    | chef | scientist    |
| Cigar   | aristoff | dannemann | ritmeester  | cain |
| Game           | domino   | mah-jongg    | bridge        | snooker   |

