.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, motorbike, roller, airplane
House: wooden, tower, victorian, modern
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, rose, begonia, azalea
1. the person driving the bike is on the far left or far right##3
2. the tower house is on the left of the wooden house##1
3. the person who growsazalea is on the left or right of the victorian house##3
4. the tower house is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the roller is on the right of the wooden house##1
6. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the tower house##1
7. the person who growsrose is on the left of the tower house##1
8. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person who growsrose##3
9. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Transport      | bike                | airplane  | motorbike | roller   |
| House           | modern | tower | wooden   | victorian |
| Flower   | rose         | zinnia     | azalea     | begonia |

