.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, balloon-flower, tulip, amaryllis
City: san-francisco, liverpool, marseilles, london
4 different games are played: canasta, poker, domino, bridge
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
2. the person who growstulip is on the far left##1
3. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
4. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
5. the person playing canasta is between the person traveling to london and the person playing bridge##2
6. the person traveling to marseilles is in an even position##4
7. the person who growsbegonia is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Flower          | tulip    | balloon-flower  | amaryllis  | begonia |
| City   | london | liverpool | san-francisco | marseilles |
| Game   | domino    | canasta     | bridge    | poker |

