House: ranch-style, tower, futuristic, townhouse
City: new-york, colone, rome, prague
1. the person traveling to colone is between the person watching drama movies and the ranch-style house##2
2. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left or far right##3
3. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
4. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the tower house##1
5. the person traveling to prague is in an odd position##4
6. the person watching comedy movies is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
7. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3
8. the futuristic house is the person watching mystery movies##1
9. the townhouse house is between the person traveling to rome and the person traveling to new-york##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
