.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
4 different games are played: chess, scrabble, billiard, domino
There 4 different types of food: carrot, peach, cauliflower, grapes
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, amaryllis, daisy, begonia
1. the person playing billiard is in an even position##4
2. the person playing scrabble is between the person playing domino and the person who growstulip##2
3. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person playing domino is in an even position##4
5. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
6. the person eating grapes is between the person who growstulip and the person eating carrot##2
7. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far right##1
8. the person eating peach is in an even position##4
9. the person who growstulip is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Game         | chess    | billiard | scrabble  | domino  |
| Food   | cauliflower | peach       | grapes | carrot |
| Flower         | daisy   | tulip      | begonia | amaryllis       |

