.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, collecting, writing, woodworking
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, taxi, quad-bike, bus
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, argentine, colombian, japanese
1. the argentine is in an even position##4
2. the argentine is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
4. the person who's hobby is writing is the person driving the bus##1
5. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far left##1
6. the person driving the ship is the argentine##1
7. the brazilian is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
8. the japanese is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| Hobby      | writing      | collecting | puzzles     | woodworking    |
| Transport   | bus | ship      | taxi | quad-bike |
| Nationality           | colombian   | argentine  | brazilian     | japanese |

