.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-16::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, go, whist, bridge
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, r&b, d&b, metal
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, egyptian, malaysian, chinese
1. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
2. the fan of jazz is in an even position##4
3. the chinese is on the far left##1
4. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
5. the person playing go is between the egyptian and the fan of d&b##2
6. the nigerian is the fan of metal##1
7. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
8. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Game    | whist    | go     | monopoly    | bridge        |
| Music-Genre       | d&b   | jazz | r&b | metal |
| Nationality   | chinese | malaysian      | egyptian    | nigerian   |

