.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-17::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, punk, pop, jazz
4 different games are played: scrabble, monopoly, canasta, domino
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, ice-hockey, golf, rowing
1. the person playing monopoly is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the fan of jazz##2
3. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
4. the fan of punk is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
6. the fan of punk is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left or far right##3
8. the fan of jazz is the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Music-Genre          | punk | jazz  | salsa   | pop    |
| Game   | scrabble  | canasta     | domino | monopoly |
| Sport   | golf   | rowing | baseball | ice-hockey   |

