.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, february, december, june
There are 4 different favourite colors: pink, aquamarine, coral, purple
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, rugby, cycling, weightlifting
1. the person who's birthday is in march is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes purple is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person who likes pink##3
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
5. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person who likes purple and the person who likes pink##2
6. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
7. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
8. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Birthday    | december    | february    | march  | june |
| Color   | purple | aquamarine | pink | coral      |
| Sport     | rugby   | volleyball        | weightlifting   | cycling       |

 